name: Okage Inu
description: Okage Inu is an ambitious project seeking to change the way the world interacts with memecoins by creating an infinitely scalable, future-proof, and highly secure ecosystem that is engineered around positive feedback loops between DEX, Chain, and Swap. Our Utilities Are: OkageSwap, OkageBridge, OkageChain. Okage Inu stealth launched with no team tokens withheld or airdrops distributed. A truely fair distribution of tokens are traded on the fair market with no max wallet - meaning that any investor may accumulate the supply. This is beneficial for the volume that funds our ecosystem and provides long-term value to our investors.
